Package: uktax
Type: Package
Title: Functions for Calculating UK Tax and Benefits for Economic Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(c("Ian","K"), "Salter",  email = "ianksalter@gmail.com", 
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package creates classes for analysing the UK Tax
    and Benefit system for tax years beginning 2016 to 2019.  
    It creates a set of calculator classes, not for every eventuality
    but rather, to illustrate discussions of the tax and benefit system.
    Version 0.1.0 focuses soley on a single employed person as a
    simplification.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
